==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Devon
<hw>De"von</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One of a breed of hardy
cattle originating in the country of Devon, England. Those of pure blood
have a deep red color. The small, longhorned variety, called <xex>North
Devons</xex>, is distinguished by the superiority of its working
oxen.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Devonian</ent>⟦br⟧
